text: Rasha Yaghi (; born 10 June 2002) is a Lebanese professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Lebanese club Safa and the Lebanon national team. ==Club career== Yaghi joined Safa in 2019; she kept four clean sheets in eight games in the 2019–20 season. == Honours and achievements == === International === Lebanon U18 * WAFF U-18 Girls Championship: 2019 ==References== ==External links== * Rasha Yaghi at Global Sports Archive * Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:People from Baalbek District Category:Lebanese women's footballers Category:Lebanon women's international footballers Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Lebanese Women's Football League players Category:Lebanon women's youth international footballers Category:Akhaa Ahli Aley FC (women) players Category:Safa WFC players
